location.fullValue: Biloxi Plan, The Pointe at Indian Ridge

data.description: Located in the highly desired Deerfield subdivision, this spacious home is move-in ready and waiting for you. This 3 bedroom / 3.5 bath home is updated with fresh interior paint, new light fixtures, ceiling fans, thermal or cordless mini blinds and custom hardwood flooring throughout. It hosts an open floor plan including the living room and family room with vaulted ceilings, gas fireplace, breakfast area and dining room with the granite kitchen (with breakfast bar) centered on the main floor. Upstairs are 3 bedrooms, 2 full bath and walk-in closets. ( includes primary suite with walk-in closet and private arched bath). The full basement seems to go on and on. It is finished with a 22' x 13' rec room ( or possibly a 4th bedroom). It also has a kitchenette, a laundry room, another full bath and a large workshop/craftroom. Another bonus... this home has 2 water heaters which is always a plus. This lower level also includes several storage cabinets, closets and 2 built in desks.... the possibilities for this space are endless. New roof in 2019.This amazing home also has a large wood deck, vinyl fenced yard (rear) and a storage shed. Beautiful landscaping with perennials and a rose garden.
